 Spanish Inquisition!\"</p><h2>Libra (Sept. 23-Oct. 22)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\" name=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>An <b>average</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Work-related travel plans might go awry today or be delayed. Efforts to deal with foreign countries, deliveries to schools, legal and medical matters and keeping schedules on track are thwarted today by unexpected obstacles.</p><h2>Scorpio (Oct. 23-Nov. 21)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\" name=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>An <b>average</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Be patient with your kids today. Likewise, romantic partners have to be patient with each other as well, especially if disputes about shared property or the cost of something arise. (People are always touchy about money.) Don't jump to conclusions. Be aware and patient to prevent potential accidents.</p><h2>Sagittarius (Nov. 22-Dec. 21)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-290000\" name=\"html-embed-module-290000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>A <b>so-so</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Patience is your best friend today because interactions with partners, spouses and close friends are completely unpredictable. They might be upset about something or do something you least expect. (Maybe you're rigid or stubborn?) If you keep cool, you are best equipped to deal with whatever happens.</p><h2>Capricorn (Dec. 22-Jan. 19)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\" name=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>An <b>average</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Work-related issues and your daily routine are up for grabs today, probably because of unexpected influences, obstacles or possible accidents. Therefore, be aware. Pay attention to everything you say and do. Nothing will unfold as expected. Be mindful and vigilant to minimize any problems that might arise.</p><h2>Aquarius (Jan. 20-Feb. 18)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\" name=\"html-embed-module-4d0000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>An <b>average</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Money issues, especially related to your kids, social outings or vacations, might blow up in your face today. It could also be a disagreement about the cost of something. You might suddenly lose your tickets or have confused directions. Something unexpected will likely occur. (Yikes!)</p><h2>Pisces (Feb. 19-March 20)</h2><div class=\"Enhancement\" data-align-center> <div class=\"HtmlModule\"><a class=\"AnchorLink\" id=\"html-embed-module-290000\" name=\"html-embed-module-290000\"></a><div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox HoroscopeStarbox_five\"> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_container\"> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> <svg class=\"HoroscopeStar\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-star\"></use></svg> </div> <div class=\"HoroscopeStarbox_description\"> <p>A <b>so-so</b> day</p> </div> </div> <style> .HoroscopeStarbox { background: #f8f8f8; display: flex; align-items: center; } .HoroscopeStarbox_container { display: grid; grid-gap: 5px; grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr 1fr; padding: 20px; width: 40%; min-width: 160px; max-width: 200px; } .HoroscopeStarbox_description { padding: 20px; font-family: var(--font-1); font-size: var(--body-2); } .HoroscopeStarbox_container svg { object-fit: cover; aspect-ratio: 1 / 1; width: 100%; } </style> </div> </div><p>Today is unpredictable, perhaps even explosive. It's also accident-prone. Therefore, keep your wits about you. Patience will be your best friend. Think before you speak or act. Don't make a big deal about anything. (Five years from now will this matter?) Take it easy.</p><h2>If today is your birthday</h2><p>Singer-songwriter Bill Withers (1938) shares your birthday. You are purposeful. Your relationships with others mean something. You are loyal, progressive and willing to defend. This is a playful, fun-loving year for you. Let your guard down, and loosen up a bit. Enjoy yourself, but don't lose sight of your goals. Old friends might reappear.</p>",
